s if I already know you.&quot;<br>
<br>
She bowed gracefully to the pair, then slid into one of the small chairs, calling to the bartender for a halfling stouter.<br>
<br>
Pushing back her hood, she ran elegantly long fingers through her close cropped hair.  &quot;A warm day, is it not?&quot; she smiled.<br>
